South African presenter, author, fitness instructor and actor Somizi has a new single with producer Mkhululi Siqula, best known as Heavy K. The track is called Ngibonile and has a slow building beat that sounds ready for the party-heavy local festive season. The song made its debut on air during The Fresh Breakfast, on Metro FM. For those who might not know Somizi is a part of the team on the radio show, led by DJ Fresh. Watch the video below: Somizi says he’d ‘kill’ Ndlozi if he went after his daughter Wuuu Shem! Somizi Weighs In On Emtee's Manhood Scandal 'I will be someone's wife.' Somizi to wed next year! Reveals his partner.